name: StudentApp
body:
### About the project
This project contains a Local Database with Students and Courses tables. The Data from these tables if fetched by WebForms (.aspx pages) here.

### Repository Information

Instructions to clone this repository in your machine:
```
$ git clone https://github.com/aditya-wate/StudentApp
```
Or Download .zip:
```
$ wget https://github.com/aditya-wate/StudentApp/archive/master.zip
```

### Authors and Contributors
Aditya Wate is a Computer Science Graduate Student at Northeastern University.

Interests: Software Engineering, Information Security, Malware Analysis.
